Yeah, into an unreadable, unmaintainable, unsupported mess.

Yeesh, my annual subscription for [[TheBrain]] just auto-renewed. It's not cheap, but then again, The Brain is so good I'm going to keep it, even though I've been using it less recently. Must admit I miss just clicking around that infinite map of my last 10 years or so. I wish there was less friction getting stuff into it. Not //zero// friction...just less.

